title: Mountain Lion (10.8.5) - Recover From Zero app/crack collection
description:
So this torrent is simply a mirror of my well-backed up collection of Mac apps collected over the years. 

its up to date - meaning pretty much every app on here is the most recent version as of this date (10/5/14 - October 5th, 2014) - however there is some caveats:

This is geared for Mountain Lion only as that is the operating system I prefer. So it contains little or no updated apps specifically for Mavericks or Yosemite. 

There are all sorts of apps in here that can be used to recover and rebuild a system that has crashed or needs rebooting/reinstalling, as well as several general purpose apps.

Feel free to just download the parts that you want and leave the rest if you want unless you are a good seeder of course.
